name: Parrotbay
description: by Marissa Wedenig / www.marissawedenig.com / digital painting and collage/ 2193px x 1632px / 2021/ A diner at the edge of the universe. Two parrots escort me to my seat . "I'd like a glass of blobertini." "blobertini?" "blobertini!" they echo "certainly." "certainly" "wormsy's on the side?" "wormsy's?"
